{"tid":1870683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解離離合合咗咁多次都係學唔識放手","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T16:42:56.000Z","uid":98372,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d11aa503e26755f6f0d01d8fd85732dd6f6e7274","tid":1870683,"uid":98372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"一齊咗半年，不停嘈交<br />\n其實大家心底都知唔夾<br />\n每次佢想走，我就出盡力挽留<br />\n諗住試多次吖？或者今次會得呢？<br />\n但其實雙方都冇改變過，問題從來冇解決過<br />\n<br />\n後來我都好攰，唔想再試，唔再挽留<br />\n大家嘗試做返朋友<br />\n但始終溝通唔到，相處唔到<br />\n最後連朋友都做唔到，佢都憎咗我<br />\n<br />\n以為自己ready放手<br />\n以為就算100%失去佢都冇所謂<br />\n但原來唔係<br />\n原來仲係會好心痛，好後悔，好自責<br />\n但無論我講咩都冇用了<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e14920e7ceab656bfdc97af21bf4f41a37f87c","tid":1870683,"uid":210414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"就算冇分手 其實你都知你哋唔會一齊得耐"},{"pid":"748b21d3dbfc233d565abeedf0c9b6881cdfecb2","tid":1870683,"uid":98372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34e14920e7ceab656bfdc97af21bf4f41a37f87c","tid":1870683,"uid":210414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"就算冇分手 其實你都知你哋唔會一齊得耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"係啊&hellip;<br />\n但人就係咁，明知唔work，都係想試<br />\n奢望萬一有奇蹟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2946dcd13679a9d76603ed331b8098ba4a0a05","tid":1870683,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748b21d3dbfc233d565abeedf0c9b6881cdfecb2","tid":1870683,"uid":98372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34e14920e7ceab656bfdc97af21bf4f41a37f87c","tid":1870683,"uid":210414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"就算冇分手 其實你都知你哋唔會一齊得耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"係啊&hellip;<br />\n但人就係咁，明知唔work，都係想試<br />\n奢望萬一有奇蹟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h